2014-01-02  Glenn Randers-Pehrson  <glennrp@simple.dallas.tx.us>

	* coders/png.c (ReadOnePNGImage): Use png_strip_16_to_8() in
	preference to png_set_scale_16_to_8() when scaling 16-bit input
	PNG down to 8-bit in a Q8 build.  "scale" is more accurate than
	"strip", but the slight difference causes reference tests to fail.

